label: CASHORDERTYPENAME
description: This field stores the descriptive name for the cash order type.

label: VENDORNUMBER
description: This field stores the credit union defined number of the vendor from the Cash Order Vendor Parameters.

label: ORDERLIMITING
description: This field stores a code that indicates the maximum number of non-cancelled orders allowed per delivery date for this order type for a site.

label: DELFREQUENCY
description: This field stores a code that defines how often a site receives delivery for this order type.

label: LOCATIONCODE
description: This field stores special vendor-specific information that identifies the site's location to this vendor.

label: CASHORDERTYPEMINORDER
description: This field stores the minimum amount required for this order.

label: CASHORDERTYPEMAXORDER
description: This field stores the maximum amount required for this order.

label: CASHORDERTYPEDELCHARGE
description: This field stores the amount the vendor charges for this order type for a normal delivery.

label: CASHORDERTYPESPECDELCHARGE
description: This field stores the amount the vendor charges for this order type for a special delivery.

label: APPLYHANDLINGFEE
description: This field stores a code that indicates whether this order type incurs a special handling fee (using the amount from the Special Handling Fee parameter in the Cash Order Vendor Parameters).

label: SPECIALHANDLINGFEE
description: This field contains the amount of special handling fee.

label: CASHORDERTYPECOMMENT:1
description: These fields each store a default comment line on this cash order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECOMMENT:2
description: These fields each store a default comment line on this cash order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECOMMENT:3
description: These fields each store a default comment line on this cash order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECOMMENT:4
description: These fields each store a default comment line on this cash order type.

label: ACTIVEFLAG
description: This field stores a code that indicates the state of this cash order type.

label: CLOSEDATE
description: This field stores the date you closed this Cash Order Type record.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: This field stores the system date in this field when you create, change, or save the Cash Order Type record. Sometimes Symitar Quest updates this field because the record was saved, even though there may not be any actual changes in the record.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:1
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Sunday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:2
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Monday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:3
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Tuesday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:4
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Wednesday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:5
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Thursday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:6
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Friday.

label: DELIVERYDAYS:7
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the vendor delivers to this site on Saturday.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:1

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:2
description: This field stores the cash value of used fifty-dollar bills (fit for circulation) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:3

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:4
description: This field stores the cash value of used ten-dollar bills (fit for circulation) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:5
description: This field stores the cash value of used five-dollar bills (fit for circulation) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:6
description: This field stores the cash value of used two-dollar bills (fit for circulation) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRFIT:7
description: This field stores the cash value of used one-dollar bills (fit for circulation) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:2
description: This field stores the cash value of new fifty-dollar bills (uncirculated) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:3

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:4
description: This field stores the cash value of new ten-dollar bills (uncirculated) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:5
description: This field stores the cash value of new five-dollar bills (uncirculated) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:6
description: This field stores the cash value of new two-dollar bills (uncirculated) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECURRNEW:7
description: This field stores the cash value of new one-dollar bills (uncirculated) in this order type.

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINROLL:4

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINROLL:5

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINROLL:7

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINBAG:2

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINBAG:3

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINBAG:4

label: CASHORDERTYPECOINBAG:5

label: LOCATOR
description: This field stores a unique number within each Cash Order Type record set that can be used as a unique identification of this record.
